"""
SDDL Decode - XSIAM Automation
Parses Security Descriptor Definition Language strings into human-readable output.

Input args:
    sddl (str): The SDDL string from an AD event (e.g., 5136 AttributeValue)
    domain_sid (str, optional): The domain SID for resolving DA/EA/etc. principals

Returns:
    dict with keys: owner, group, dacl_flags, sacl_flags, aces (list of decoded ACE dicts),
    raw_sddl, summary (human-readable text block)
"""

